# Design system

The always-on source of truth is **`../.cursor/rules/design.mdc`** (workspace root).

That file defines the v3 token set, three-tier surface taxonomy (app chrome / emotional
surfaces / website templates), type scale, component inventory, and emotional-surface
primitives. Match `design/theme-direction.html` for app chrome and `design/reference.html`
for component + primitive detail.
